. Place Varoma with chicken into position, secure Varoma lid and steam <b>12 min\/Varoma\/speed 4<b>."},{"content":"Divide asparagus and cherry tomatoes between Varoma dish and tray around chicken. Season with salt and pepper, secure Varoma lid and steam <b>6 min\/Varoma\/speed 4<b> or until vegetables and chicken are cooked to your liking."},{"content":"Serve chicken and vegetables with reserved risoni and extra basil pesto (optional), if desired."}],"hintsAndTricks":["To make your own basil pesto, please refer to the recipe in <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i>."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","40m","4 portions"]}